transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra. This is Jimmy. How can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Yeah. I had ordered some stuff from you guys. It got screwed up.

Speaker 1: My credit card number was messed up.

Speaker 2: So when I put in a new credit card, you guys automatically ordered me something.

Speaker 1: I was going for the new Viagra, and you guys ordered me something else.

Speaker 2: I called, spoke to somebody.

Speaker 1: They swapped that, canceled my other order, and just sent me that new Viagra.

Speaker 2: They said they were going to get rid of the charges at a $200-and-something charge on my account.

Speaker 1: Okay. Let me get you over to the rep that you talked to. Hold on one second.

Speaker 2: Give me one second.

Speaker 1: Okay.
